secubox-soc-gateway (1.1.0-1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Phase 5: Hierarchical Mode Implementation
  * New features:
    - Mode configuration (edge/regional/central)
    - Regional SOC enrollment and token management
    - Regional-to-central aggregation with signed push
    - Cross-region threat correlation
    - Global summary and regional breakdown APIs
    - Multi-tier hierarchy support
  * API endpoints added:
    - GET /hierarchy/status
    - POST /hierarchy/mode
    - POST /regional/token
    - POST /regional/enroll
    - POST /regional/ingest
    - GET /regional/socs
    - POST /upstream/enroll
    - GET /upstream/status
    - GET /global/summary
    - GET /global/regions
    - GET /global/threats

