secubox-soc-gateway (1.0.0-1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Implements SOC Gateway for fleet monitoring
  * Features:
    - Node registration with HMAC enrollment tokens
    - Fleet-wide metrics aggregation
    - Unified alert stream from all nodes
    - Cross-node threat correlation
    - Remote command execution with audit
    - WebSocket real-time updates
    - Hierarchical deployment support

